【Weekender and Travel Bag】This duffle bag for women is designed to be both fashionable and practical. It can be used as a men's gym sports bag, school luggage bag, travel carry on bag, travel handbag, or gym tote bag, suitable for exercise, travel, sports activities, tennis, basketball, yoga, fishing, hunting, camping, hiking, and many outdoor activities.
